faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 2016年11月開始失眠<br />\n本身家母有焦慮症<br />\n所以佢有啲spare 既安眠藥俾我食<br />\n食食下食到而家<br />\n多數係食半粒<br />\n有時第日如果有緊要野做<br />\n或者要早起身番工<br />\n會食一粒<br />\n不過都keep 到最多食一粒<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n阿媽話呢啲冇得睇醫生<br />\n要排政府睇都有排排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以從來都冇因為失眠而睇過醫生<br />\n<br />\n一直都好想有人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以終於忍唔住入黎取下暖<br />\n一撻落床就訓到死豬咁既人係唔會明我地感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a031fde26a3f71caf8d3e67083d49c543c6782","tid":976951,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:02:08.000Z","msg":"食benzos?生理性依賴"},{"pid":"277d82b3f1812e6e93d4221f0b949aaf04aa23aa","tid":976951,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"061d1c68352fbcd200d7749a90ebbffc4f143d59","tid":976951,"uid":136933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d31306d4979a28fc6dc484b2565830b27568d97","tid":976951,"uid":200633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8742ce6792989279fce1652b69f46b2d36b45400","tid":976951,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T19:41:04.000Z","msg":"一冇藥係身就訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好廢 覺得自己好病態<br />\n飲酒隊草都冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一啲幫助都冇<br />\n唔係唔想靠自己訓<br />\n一黎冇呢個時間比我去試訓<br />\n二黎唔食藥個人會好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"你提左我未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm